        "## Reading and Merging Files\n",
        "The files use `::` as a separator. We give proper column names while reading,\n",
        "then merge ratings + users + movies into one consolidated dataframe."
      ],
      "metadata": {
        "id": "xSNmYdNAkuNJ"
