      "source": [
        "## EDA, Data Cleaning & Feature Engineering\n",
        "\n",
        "We review the structure of the dataset, check for missing values and duplicates,\n",
        "perform type conversions, map the coded columns (Age, Occupation) to readable labels,\n",
        "and derive a new feature `ReleaseYear` (and `Decade`) from the movie title."
      ],
      "metadata": {
        "id": "A04-sRfuoLkl"
      }
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
